name: Dud Bolt's Podracer
Lore: 'RS 557 Podracer. Secretly hired by Sebulba to protect him during Podraces.',
Text: 'Deploy on Podrace Arena. Adds 1 to each of your race destinies here. If Sebulba''s Podracer on table, may lose this Podracer to cancel Losing Track or Neck And Neck; place all race destinies here in owner''s Used Pile.',
